<subSubSection id="C368652E93518E0CF2AAFC65FB04FBFE" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593518E0CF2AAFC65FB04FBFE" blockId="8.[151,1437,1015,1257]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893518E0CF2AAFC65FB00FBFE" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147325" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793518E0CF02FFC65FDA8FBDA" box="[530,633,1015,1041]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels: “male symbol”, “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693518E0CF6B5FC65FAC7FBDA" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[1160,1302,1015,1041]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="meridionalis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793518E0CF6B5FC65FAC7FBDA" box="[1160,1302,1015,1041]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">meridionalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in Galia merid.” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793518E0CF311FB89FE4EFBFE" box="[300,415,1051,1077]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693518E0CF3F9FB89FC0CFBFE" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[452,989,1051,1077]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="meridionalis" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793518E0CF3F9FB89FC93FBFE" box="[452,834,1051,1077]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Harpalus (Ophonus) meridionalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF175FB89FC0CFBFE" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[840,989,1051,1077]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393518E0CF66CFB89FB17FBFE" box="[1105,1222,1051,1077]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93518E0CF2FAFBADFE42FB22" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593518E0CF2FAFBADFA80FB6A" blockId="8.[151,1437,1015,1257]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
According to Dejean, 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693518E0CF3FEFBADFDA4FB92" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[451,629,1087,1113]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="meridionalis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793518E0CF3FEFBADFDA4FB92" box="[451,629,1087,1113]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">O. meridionalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693518E0CF093FBADFCBBFB92" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[686,874,1087,1113]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subquadratus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793518E0CF093FBADFCBBFB92" box="[686,874,1087,1113]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">O. subquadratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were collected in the same area. The former was synonymized by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF363FBF1FD96FBB5" author="Jeannel, R." box="[350,583,1123,1150]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942: 644)</bibRefCitation>
, a criterion followed by other entomologists (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF65DFBF1FACCFBB6" author="Sciaky, R." box="[1120,1309,1123,1149]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky,1987: 62</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF711FBF1FEE5FB6A" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
). Keys to determine the species are found in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF116FB15FC02FB6A" author="Jeannel, R." box="[811,979,1159,1185]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF1E2FB15FBADFB6A" author="Sciaky, R." box="[991,1148,1159,1185]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky (1987)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF68FFB15FA9DFB6A" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1202,1356,1159,1185]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">Wrase (2011)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593518E0CF2FAFB39FE42FB22" blockId="8.[151,1437,1015,1257]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
The species is distributed in Central Europe, the Mediterranean Basin and from 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593518E0CF679FB39FB75FB0E" box="[1092,1188,1195,1221]" name="Turkey" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Anatolia</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593518E0CF6FAFB39FAB3FB0E" box="[1223,1378,1195,1221]" name="Turkmenistan" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">Turkmenistan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF74CFB39FE57FB22" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
